    "system": {
        "description": {
            "value": "<p><em>You smile widely, kiss the heart of a hen, and repeatedly whisper words meant to menace your foes. Affected creatures see an image of their worst fears writhe into existence, crawling from your mouth into the space before them. The sight causes your foes to flee in terror from the dreadful apparitions.</em></p><p><strong>Wisdom Save</strong> </p><ul><li><p><strong>Failure:</strong> The target is &amp;reference[Frightened]{frightened}, and must use their movement to move away from you by the safest available route on each of their turns, unless there is nowhere further to move.<span>Target rolls again at end of their turns, ending effect on success.</span></p></li><li><p><strong>Success:</strong> No effect.</p></li></ul>",
            "chat": "<strong>Wisdom Save</strong> </p><ul><li><p><strong>Failure:</strong> The target is &amp;reference[Frightened]{frightened}, and must use their movement to move away from you by the safest available route on each of their turns, unless there is nowhere further to move.<span>Target rolls again at end of their turns, ending effect on success.</span></p></li><li><p><strong>Success:</strong> No effect.</p></li></ul>"
